sellerCard.oneLiner: Empower Your Business with Seamless Mobile App and Website Development
sellerCard.description:
With over 10 years of experience in mobile app development, I specialize in creating high-quality Android and iOS apps using Flutter. My expertise spans the latest technologies, including Flutter and Nodejs
I have successfully developed a diverse range of applications, from appointment booking and dating apps to video streaming, VOIP audio/video calls, e-commerce, and car/taxi rental solutions. Leveraging my extensive experience and cutting-edge skills, I deliver innovative and reliable mobile app solutions tailored to meet your unique needs.

description.content:
Are you looking for a stunning, responsive, and user-friendly website that stands out? I'm here to help! My team and I offer professional website design and development services that are perfect for small businesses, startups, and personal projects.


Custom Web Development For:

  • E-commerce App
  • Appointment Booking Website for Taxi, Car Rental & Salon and Spa
  • Chat web app for Dating web, Astrologer, Customer ticket support, social media
  • Data Dashboard for any business like employee monthly statistics, daily product production management, Daily order management portals


Technologies We Use:

  • Programming Language: JavaScript
  • Frontend Development: React.js, Jquery, TypeScript
  • HTML5, CSS3, Tailwind CSS, JavaScript
  • Backend Development: Node.js - Express, Socket.io
  • Databases - MYSQL, MongoDB
  • Server: VPS, Dedicated


Benefits to go with me:

  • Well, Define the workflow for the project.
  • Milestone based order
  • Provide source code with proper documentation
  • The Figma source file provides
  • Weekly Meeting discussion
  • Maintainance and support(Hourly/Month)


Get Started Today!


Ready to bring your vision to life? Contact me now, and let's create something amazing together! Free Zoom consultation available.

slide.name: build, rebuild website development as full stack developer, front end developer

questionsAndAnswers.question: How do I get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Getting started is easy! Contact us to schedule a free Zoom consultation where we can discuss your project in detail and provide a tailored quote.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What services do you offer?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We offer comprehensive website development services, including custom website design, responsive development, e-commerce integration, content management systems (CMS), and ongoing maintenance and support.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How long does it take to build a website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The timeline depends on the complexity of the project. A simple website may take 2-4 weeks, while more complex sites, like e-commerce platforms, could take 6-8 weeks or more. We'll provide a more accurate estimate after discussing your specific needs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What platform do you use to build websites?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We specialize in platforms like React.js, Node.js, and custom-coded solutions, depending on your requirements and preferences.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How much will my website cost?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The cost varies based on the project's complexity, features, and design requirements. We offer competitive pricing and can provide a detailed quote after understanding your needs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website be mobile-friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, all our websites are designed to be fully responsive, meaning they will look and function well on desktops, tablets, and smartphones.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide website hosting and domain registration?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We can assist you in choosing and setting up a hosting provider and registering a domain name, but these services are typically handled separately from development.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I update the website myself after it's built?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Absolutely! We build our websites on user-friendly CMS platforms, making it easy for you to update content, add new pages, or make changes without needing technical expertise.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I need help after the website is live?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: We offer ongoing maintenance and support packages to keep your website running smoothly. Whether it's updates, security monitoring, or troubleshooting, we're here to help.
